Abkhaz 
conflict is defining Abkhazia's political status. 
  The Council of Ministers of the autonomous republic of 
Abkhazia hopes that the Boris Yeltsin-Eduard Shevardnadze 
meeting and the signing of a package of documents will be useful 
not only for Georgia but also for Russia. 

