  [Text] The Abkhazian Defense Ministry reported on 
continuing acts of sabotage committed by the Georgian formations 
in the Abkhazian region of Ghali. 
  The ministry's statement published on Thursday says that as 
many as 3 Abkhazian servicemen were killed during an act of 
