  The document underlined that this displayed the Georgian 
formations' intention to destabilize the situation in the region 
of Ghali and to block the Abkhazian troops defending the 
Abkhazian- Georgian border on the Inguri River. 
  The Abkhazian Defense Ministry announced that it could "not 
ignore all these facts and would undertake the appropriate 
measures." 

