<H3> <TI>   President Nazarbayev Approves 1994 Budget </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0302173194 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 1500 GMT 
3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0302173194 </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty Kazakh Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Kazakh </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In accordance with the law of the Republic of 
Kazakhstan dated 10 December 1993, with regard to the temporary 
delegation of additional powers to the president of the Republic 
of Kazakhstan and heads of local administrations, the president 
of Kazakhstan, by his decree, has endorsed the republican budget 
for 1994. 
  The budget has been presented by the Kazakhstan government. 
The revenues total a figure of 40,299,685,000 tenge, and its 
expenditures 48,111,806,000 tenge; the maximum size of the 
deficit stands at 7,812,121,000 tenge. 

</TEXT>

