Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Riga, Feb 03, BNS -- A NATO delegation is coming to 
Riga Thursday [3 February] on a two-day trip to meet with the 
Latvian working group for the Partnership for Peace program. 
  The groups will discuss Latvia's signature to the 
