<H3> <TI>   Air Force Bombing of Karabakh Reported </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0302144294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1408 GMT 
3 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0302144294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] We have just received a report by the LUR agency 
that the Azerbaijani air force is bombing towns and villages in 
Nagorno-Karabakh. At 1100 hours, the Azerbaijani air force 
violated the airspace of the Nagorno-Karabakh Republic and 
carried out an air strike against several populated localities 
in Askeranskiy rayon. Casualty figures are being clarified. 

</TEXT>

