<F P=100> National Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Crimean President Meshkov Inaugurated 4 Feb </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0402095194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0936 GMT 4 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0402095194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Efim Shvartsman] </F>
  [Text] Simferopol February 4 TASS -- Yuriy Meshkov, who was 
elected the first president of the Crimea, was inaugurated on 
Friday at a session of the parliament of the peninsula. 
  The 49-year old lawyer put his hand on the constitution of 
the Crimea and the human rights declaration and read out the 
oath of the president. 
  He said his actions would be based on people's will and law. 

</TEXT>

