<H3> <TI>   Tatarstan President's Moscow Visit Postponed </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0502123394 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1204 
GMT 5 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0502123394 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By unidentified ITAR-TASS correspondent] </F>
  [Text] Moscow, 5 Feb -- Reports by some mass media that 
President Mintimer Shaymiyev of Tatarstan has arrived in Moscow 
and is to have a meeting today with President Boris Yeltsin of 
the Russian Federation are factually incorrect, an ITAR-TASS 
correspondent learned at Tatarstan's permanent mission in Moscow. 
  Such a meeting was indeed planned, the diplomat on duty at 
the mission pointed out, but for a number of reasons it has been 
postponed until a new date can be set. 

</TEXT>

