Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Units of the Chechen armed opposition have 
surrounded General Dudayev's residence in Groznyy, ANI agency 
reports. The leader of the opposition, Gen. Ibrahim Suleymenov 
has ordered combat maneuvers to be started near Dudayev's 
