<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Efim Shvartsman] </F>
  [Text] Kiev February 4 TASS -- Ukrainian President Leonid 
Kravchuk met on Friday the first popularly elected president of 
the Crimean semi-autonomous republic Yuriy Meshkov. 
  Meshkov arrived in the Ukrainian capital after his 
inauguration ceremony in the Crimean administrative centre of 
