<F P=102>  LD0402195694 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1638 
GMT 4 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0402195694 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Boris Maynayev] </F>
  [Text] Bishkek, 4 Feb -- The Central Electoral Commission 
of the Republic of Kyrgyzstan today announced the final results 
of the nationwide referendum on confidence in President Askar 
Akayev. The referendum was held on 30 January. 
  A total of 2,176,000 people took part in the poll. This is 
