<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Officials Regret Refusing Grachev Troop Offer </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0402141494 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1200 GMT 4 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0402141494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, 4 Feb -- According to the IBERIA news 
agency, representatives of the Georgian side told Russia's 
Defense Minister Pavel Grachev, during his visit to Tbilisi, 
that Georgia had earlier made a mistake by not accepting his 
offer to introduce two Russian divisions and a brigade into the 
Abkhaz region. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

<DOC>
<DOCNO> FBIS3-36518 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drsov025_s_94011" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-SOV-94-025 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
